{"tid":772312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有事鐘無豔] 中國政府下令停辦慰安婦問題國際研討會","createTime":"2018-08-08T15:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T15:35:29.000Z","uid":119393,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f7fd230bbd13f20913a7b96d1d02465377542e","tid":772312,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】內地上海師範大學原定周五舉辦的慰安婦問題國際研討會，據報被外交部要求停辦。<br />\n<br />\n共同社引述上海師範大學中國慰安婦問題研究中心表示，今個月接獲外交部要求停辦研討會。中心指，研討會的日程早在半年前已決定，原定會有中日韓朝及美國等專家大約60人出席，目前不清楚可否改期舉行，上海師範大學設有中國首座慰安婦歷史博物館。<br />\n<br />\n分析認為，今次官方叫停慰安婦問題研討會是顧及日方星期日正值中日和平友好條約締結40周年，中日外長月初在新加坡會談期間，亦就加速協調首相安倍晉三年內訪華達成共識。"},{"pid":"efe88690a498808be62b14b6f8213d6b54550eab","tid":772312,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaa00f8a69aeaaa2720f7869623684aeb5df1a0","tid":772312,"uid":50457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜唔係要人道歉到2046？"},{"pid":"3a0190b44d372b69b9b1d6622ed719de3c333f5b","tid":772312,"uid":44454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:09:45.000Z","msg":"之前係日本肉便器，依家係中國肉便器"},{"pid":"38617327be5a61033f6225404cd974222521b2db","tid":772312,"uid":55533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那女人天生係雞"},{"pid":"57076b72302167781a94f5eb9cff415a1fa79e62","tid":772312,"uid":54337,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:25:53.000Z","msg":"有事就中日友好<br />\n無事就手撕鬼子"},{"pid":"11111a7def5cebeb67f6a140817c13895ec3d7d1","tid":772312,"uid":62950,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-